or 0.02 percent, to 32,058.97 at the close in Johannesburg.  The Bidvest Group Ltd.  (BVT SJ): The diversified investment
group with assets in financial services and auto dealerships
said late yesterday it bought fresh fish producer and
distributor Seafood Holdings Ltd. for an enterprise value of 45
million pounds ($69.2 million). Bidvest rose for the third day
in four, adding 3.15 rand, or 2 percent, to 159.15 rand.  Platmin Ltd.  (PLN SJ): The platinum mining company said it
had agreed with the holders of its $135 million convertible
debentures to extend their maturity to Feb. 28, 2011. Platmin
declined 10 cents, or 1.7 percent, to 5.70 rand.  Shares or American depositary receipts of the following
